OL,3,CBelfast City Council introduces new
OL,4,Cbin tagging system
OL,6,FThe city-wide scheme is being
OL,7,Fintroduced on a phased basis to give
OL,8,Fhouseholders time to get used to
OL,9,Fbinning their rubbish without any risk
OL,10,Fto workers or the environment.
OL,12,FCouncillor Ruth Brooks, Chair of
OL,13,FBelfast City Council's People and
OL,14,FCommunities Committee said:
OL,16,F"This is an updated bin policy that
OL,17,Fhas been coming through our committee
OL,18,Ffor some time.
