OL,3,CBelfast City Council introduces new
OL,4,Cbin tagging system
OL,6,F"It relates to bins that are
OL,7,Foverfilled, bins that are
OL,8,Fcontaminated, or some bins that have a
OL,9,Fbin liner in them.
OL,11,F"Unfortunately, there have been some
OL,12,Fincidents involving these from a
OL,13,Fhealth and safety perspective.
OL,15,F"Any of the bins that are presented in
OL,16,Fa poor manner will be amber tagged.
OL,18,F"That is just a warning that we will
OL,19,Faccept your bin today but in future,
OL,20,Fwe will not."
