OL,3,CBelfast City Council introduces new
OL,4,Cbin tagging system
OL,6,FHouseholders have until the end of
OL,7,FSeptember to get used to the new rules.
OL,9,FBins which are persistently
OL,10,Foverflowing or lined will eventually
OL,11,Freceive a red tag, and red tagged bins
OL,12,Fwill not be emptied.
